properties.full_description: The Danby Designer 11 cu. ft. all refrigerator is great for people who are looking for a reliable and dependable refrigerator unit without freezer space. The stylish appliance features a single door with an integrated handle and a clever reversible hinge which allows you to set it for right or left-handed opening. The neat and tidy interior is illuminated by a powerful lighting system which makes it easy to organize the glass-covered vegetable crisper, the integrated door shelves, and the four-and-a-half adjustable glass shelves. There’s considerable room for large and tall bottle and this top-of-the-line unit comes with a worry-free 18-month warranty on parts and labor along with convenient in-home service.
